    <h1>Conversion Funnel</h1>
    <p class="description">A step-by-step map of how visitors move from first click to completed action. Reveals where <strong>up to 70% of prospects drop off</strong> and where a single fix compounds revenue.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
